data.title: News
data.text:
The Ambassador of the State of Qatar receives the UNICEF representative in Djibouti

13 September 2023

His Excellency Dr. Rashid bin Shafeea Al Marri, Ambassador of the State of Qatar to the Republic of Djibouti, received in his office at the embassy, Mr. Beate Dastel, representative of the United Nations Children’s Fund (UNICEF) in Djibouti.

The Ambassador of the State of Qatar receives the Resident Coordinator of the United Nations agencies in Djibouti

11 September 2023

His Excellency Dr. Rashid bin Shafeea Al Marri, Ambassador of the State of Qatar to the Republic of Djibouti, received in his office at the embassy, Mr. Jose Barahona, Resident Coordinator of the United Nations Agency in Djibouti.

The Ambassador of the State of Qatar in Djibouti receives the Ambassador of Sudan

04 September 2023

His Excellency Dr. Rashid bin Shafeea Al Marri, Ambassador of the State of Qatar to the Republic of Djibouti, received, at the embassy His Excellency Ambassador Rahma Saleh Al-Obaid, Ambassador of the Republic of Sudan to Djibouti.

The Ambassador of the State of Qatar meets with the Director of the Arab World Department at the Ministry of Foreign Affairs in Djibouti

14 June 2023

His Excellency Dr. Rashid bin Shafeea Al -Marri, Ambassador of the State of Qatar to the Republic of Djibouti, met with Mr. Mohamed Dualeh Waleh, Director of the Arab World Department at the Ministry of Foreign Affairs in Djibouti.

The Embassy of the State of Qatar holds an Iftar for those fasting at the Doha Mosque in Djibouti

19 April 2023

The Embassy of the State of Qatar in the Republic of Djibouti, in cooperation with the office of the Qatar Charity Association, held a Ramadan Iftar for those fasting at the Doha Mosque in Djibouti for the year 1444 AH - 2023.

His Highness the Amir sends a message to the President of the Republic of Djibouti

13 April 2023

His Highness Sheikh Tamim bin Hamad Al Thani Amir of the State of Qatar, sent a written message to His Excellency President Ismail Omar Guelleh, President of the Republic of Djibouti, related to bilateral relations between the two brotherly countries, and ways to support and enhance them.

Launch of the investment guide in Qatar in ten languages

13 April 2023

The Qatar Investment Promotion Agency has recently launched a number of guides, including the main guide: “Investment Guide in Qatar” in Arabic, English, Chinese, (Mandarin), Czech, French, German, Italian, Japanese, Russian and Spanish.

The Speaker of Parliament in Djibouti meets with the Ambassador of the State of Qatar

22 March 2023

His Excellency Mr. Dileita Mohamed Dileita, Speaker of the House of Representatives of the Republic of Djibouti, met with His Excellency Dr. Rashid bin Shafeea al-Mari, Ambassador of the State of Qatar to Djibouti.

The Minister of Social Affairs and Solidarity of Djibouti meets with the Ambassador of the State of Qatar

02 February 2023

HE Mrs. Olofah Ismail Abdou, Minister of Social Affairs and Solidarity of the Republic of Djibouti, met with HE Dr. Rashid bin Shafeea Al Marri, Ambassador of the State of Qatar to Djibouti.
